parameters:
Student: "Welcome! To the academy! With the two of you here,
it's as if we have the strength of a hundred people♪"

\F[tou_oti]Daidai: "Of course. With my arrival, this school will soon
become the property of our cult♪ That makes it the seventh
school."

\F[tou_oti]\FF[mikan_oti]\AA[2]Mikan: "Well, we had to cry to the guru for help with three
schools, so it's half and half... But we'll do our best for
the guru!"

Student: "I've heard that students are the guru's favorite,
yet I can't seem to be of any use... It's so painful..."

\F[tou_oti]Daidai: "Those who don't understand the nobility of living
by the teachings of the Ecstatic Cloth Fringe Cult are truly
unfortunate. We need to convey this properly."

\F[tou_oti]Daidai: "We'll show them. The happiness of being a disciple
who reveres the guru and seeks his teachings♪"

\F[tou_oti]\FF[mikan_oti]\AA[2]Mikan: "There's also a manual that the guru made for us.
Please take a look at it. Even seduction can be quite
pleasant♪"

Student: "Ye-yes! Thank you very much!! Can someone with my
meager body be of use to the cult?"

\F[tou_oti]Daidai: "Don't worry. If you have faith and enthusiasm for
the guru, sex appeal will follow♪ Men are easy to conquer
once you slide a finger down their crotch♪"

\F[tou_oti]\FF[mikan_oti]\AA[2]Mikan: "Just whispering about the joy of becoming a believer
is effective too♪ Everyone listens trembling with ecstasy as
if they're ascending to heaven♪"

Student: "I'm feeling encouraged! I'll help out as much as I
can, even if I'm not much!"

\F[tou_oti]Daidai: "Thank you. Now... let's convert the entire academy.
Starting with the student council... then the staff room."

\F[tou_oti]\FF[mikan_oti]\AA[2]Mikan: "Top-down is fundamental♪ Will you guide us...
please?"
Student: "Yes! This way, please...!!"

★Music by hasegawairue-sama, Nota no Mori-sama, Yūfuruka-
sama
